# Group Authentication
This API uses [Basic Authentication](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Basic_access_authentication) for its authentication.

## Ping [/ping]
Ping can be used to make sure your implementation of authentication is working as expected.

In this document, you can click links that look like the one below to get a full description and an example of the request and response for the given endpoint.

